highest, and to also share why it gave those scores. So there's a paragraph trying to make the case

67
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:08,700
that dogs are better than cats as pets. And then there's another paragraph trying to make the case

68
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:14,140
that cats are better than dogs. And then finally a paragraph that says neither dogs or cats are

69
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:18,800
better. They're both great. And the chatbot outputs a score for each paragraph as well as an

70
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:24,780
explanation for each score. You can also chat with a chatbot. And by that, I mean you can have an

71
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:30,219
ongoing back and forth conversation. And there are ways you can start these conversations so that

72
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:34,180
you're not the only one moving the conversation forward, but you can actually have the chatbot

73
00:06:34,460 --> 00:06:39,380
ask follow-up questions or take the initiative in leading the conversation. You'll learn more about

74
