follow-up questions and making suggestions for what I can think about or talk about next. You can also

77
00:06:55,260 --> 00:07:01,440
use chatbots to take actions beyond just outputting text. An AI-enabled feature that is very related

78
00:07:01,740 --> 00:07:06,940
to today's chatbots is a personal assistant. You can use a personal assistant on your phone

79
00:07:07,420 --> 00:07:13,060
to set a calendar event or send a text message to a friend. And a lot of chatbots now are also

80
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:18,780
able to connect to other software so that they can, for instance, search the internet to help

81
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:23,600
them answer your question. Here's an example of taking action by using a personal assistant.

